cate 结婚证","headword":"marriage certificate"},{"type":"entry","text":"shotgun wedding 奉子成婚","headword":"shotgun wedding"},{"type":"entry","text":"flash marriage 闪婚","headword":"flash marriage"},{"type":"entry","text":"destination wedding 旅行结婚","headword":"destination wedding"},{"type":"entry","text":"anniversary [ˌænɪˈvɜːsəri]","headword":"anniversary"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.周年纪念"},{"type":"note","text":"◎marriage anniversary结婚周年纪念日"},{"type":"entry","text":"paper wedding 纸婚（1周年）","headword":"paper wedding"},{"type":"entry","text":"silver wedding 银婚（25周年）","headword":"silver wedding"},{"type":"entry","text":"golden wedding 金婚（50周年）","headword":"golden wedding"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Congratulations! What gift should I get for the future bride?（祝"},{"type":"text","text":"贺你们！我该送未来的新娘什么礼物呢？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Oh, just your presence is important!（噢，重要的是你的出"},{"type":"text","text":"席！）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"}]},{"number":227,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：They're going to honeymoon in Europe. （他们打算去欧洲度蜜"},{"type":"text","text":"月。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：How nice. （真好。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 3"},{"type":"example","text":"A：The dowry of my wife was very little in that age. （那个年代，"},{"type":"text","text":"我妻子的嫁妆很少。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：What's for that? （都有些什么呀？）"},{"type":"example","text":"A：New three pieces, television, washing machine and refrigerator."},{"type":"text","text":"（新三件，电视机、洗衣机和电冰箱。）"}]}]}